scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"well as in energy saving mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"role":"symbol"}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage","op":"replace","value":"occ"},{"path":"\/metadata\/roleHeading","op":"replace","value":"Instance Property"},{"path":"\/metadata\/title","op":"replace","value":"energyConfiguration"},{"path":"\/metadata\/symbolKind","op":"replace","value":"property"},{"path":"\/metadata\/fragments","op":"replace","value":[{"text":"energyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]},{"path":"\/topi